description:
In July 2014, Stéphane Mercier met Quincy Jones at Jazz à Vienne (France), we taped that message and went back to Toots in Belgium...very moving to see two giants sharing such a friendship over the years.
Produced by Avalon productions. Directed by Michael Pierrard, Cameras: Samy Lamloum, André Bontems, assisted by Emilie Boumal & Hélène Dereppe
